en el hostal "Millbrook"...

449
00:20:16,235 --> 00:20:17,518
en Poughkeepsie.

450
00:20:21,240 --> 00:20:24,492
  

451
00:20:24,576 --> 00:20:27,462
Cuando nos estábamos
yendo, vi a Serena...

452
00:20:27,546 --> 00:20:30,414
Entrando con el Sr. Donovan.

453
